News.Title: Suntech Infra Gets ₹37.2 Million L&T Order
News.Summary: Suntech Infra Solutions secures significant ₹37.2 million work order from L&T, marking another milestone in the company's infrastructure project portfolio and strengthening its business relationship with the engineering giant.

News.Title: SunTech Infra Gets ₹176.2 Cr Order from Mundra
News.Summary: SunTech Infra Solutions secures significant work order worth ₹176.20 million from Mundra Petrochem, marking a major business development for the infrastructure company.
